    "body": "Latest FlashInfer (`0.5.3`) changes `plan` API which breaks `fast_plan_decode`.\nThis PR updates FlashInfer to the latest version and fixes API breaking by adding another argument to `self._cached_module.plan` call, corresponding to `num_colocated_ctas=0`. ",
